WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.877
Okay.

00:00:01.878 --> 00:00:04.347
Everything you have heard
about my wife...

00:00:04.505 --> 00:00:05.757
is a lie.

00:00:05.923 --> 00:00:10.019
She is a calculating,
murderous psychopath.

00:00:10.636 --> 00:00:12.058
And I have been complicit...

00:00:12.221 --> 00:00:13.347
Nick!

00:00:19.020 --> 00:00:21.022
Nick? Breakfast.

00:00:21.105 --> 00:00:22.106
Honey?

